🏴‍☠️ Ahoy Mateys! Arrrr you ready for Gassparilla 2023!! Here are some last minute FAQs to make tomorrow a fun day out for everyone.

FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS:

🔵 Can a friend check in for me? YES
Send your friend your ticket confirmation. They will then be able to pick up your wristband.

🔵 Can I check in my entire group? YES
If you ordered for a group, you or anyone in your group can check everyone in at once and pick up the wristbands.

🔵 Can I check in after Check-In closes? NO
If you cannot make it to Check-in before it closes, please have one of your friends pick up your wristband early by forwarding your ticket.

🔵 Once checked in, can I join the Crawl late? YES
After you picked up your wristbands, feel free to join the Crawl later. However, all wristband privileges (eg. free welcome shots, covers and drink specials) are not valid after the event has officially finished.

🔵 Can I buy Brunch on event day? MAYBE (Subject to availability)
"Crawl Only" ticket holders must buy a new “Brunch Ticket” and will get their original order refunded.

🔵 Can I eat brunch at any location? NO
Brunch is limited at each location. You can only have brunch at the location stated on your ticket.

🔵 Can I get from A to B without my car? YES
There are multiple ways to move between Downtown, South Tampa and Ybor or from Bar to Bar. Use Scooters, Bikes, Uber, Lyft, StreetCar or the classic: Walk ;)
We recommend to Uber or Lyft to your starting venue as parking will be limited for Gasparilla.

🔵 Where is the Big Wave Treasure Cove?
Tony Jannus Park - across from Publix on Bayshore Blvd, at the corner of Platt St & 200 Bayshore Blvd.

🔶 Time: 6pm - 8pm

You'll pick up your wristband, complete with 5 tabs for the welcome shots. No more waiting in line on the big day – just show up, beeline to the bar and let the festivities begin! 👻🍹

Top Tip: You can pick up yours AND your friends wristbands. Simply bring along their order confirmation.

See you there! 🕷️🍻

GOOD TO KNOW:
🎃 Can a friend check in for me? YES
Send your friend your ticket confirmation. They will then be able to pick up your wristband.
🎃 Can I check in after Check-In closes on event day? NO
If you cannot make it to check-in before it closes, please have one of your friends pick up your wristband early by forwarding your ticket.
🎃 Can I check in my entire group? YES
If you ordered for a group, you or anyone in your group can check everyone in at once and pick up the wristbands.
🎃 Once checked in, can I join the Crawl late? YES
After you picked up your wristbands, feel free to join the Crawl later. However, wristband privileges (welcome shots, free cover and drink specials) are not valid after the event has officially finished.

🔵 MacDinton’s Event Day Info:
While the wristband will get you in the door without a cover fee, RE-ENTRY is not permitted.
